YUVtool - application for viewing raw video sequences

This is work in progress. Application is not usable in the current state.

Build requirements:
- cmake 3.0 or later
- c++ compiler supporting C++11
- gtkmm dev libraries 3.18 or later
- sfml dev libraries 2.1 or later

Additionally, to build developers documentation, these are required:
- latex(babel with english and polish support, pdftex)
- inkscape
